snippet.title: 11th Dream - Winter Update
snippet.description:
Now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/949450/11th_Dream/
Steam Newshub: https://store.steampowered.com/news/app/949450/view/2919986982633959785

Read more on our blog: https://blog.bluepulsar.cz/11th-dream/winter-update/

In Winter Update, we are releasing Verticality, new skirmish map which makes use of our previous update! Use walls to rapidly slide up and surprise your opponents! On some maps it is snowing now - is the system freezing down?
